The party's national executive committee is meeting at Nasrec in Johannesburg for its policy conference. JOHANNESBURG - President Jacob Zuma is addressing the ANC's national policy conference in Nasrec.Delegates at this conference will be meeting in commissions to debate policy.Zuma addressed a gala dinner on Thursday night ahead of the start of the party s gathering.The president struck a conciliatory note during his speech on Thursday night, talking about the unity of the organisation and the need for leaders not to be sidetracked by their differences.WATCH: President Jacob Zuma at ANC policy conference